column5: Cant belive my little guy is 14 already.    Here is the rocket story: http://www.ofncommun...birthday+rocket
So what are you doing for ol' Rocket this year Joe? Taking him fishing maybe?
What a little cutie.  Happy Birtday Rocket!!!
Happy B'day Rocket....hope he gets you sumthin' special to munch on...
Wise looking little critter Happy B day Rocket !!!!!
Your old pal is getting a little Grahahahy Joe.  Hope you gave him a special treat today !
He got an extra ration of grain and a few roasted peanuts.His mother gave him a good headbut when he tried to snitch some of her grain.Kids these days! Joe
I was wondering why rocket was knocking on my door and wanting a piggy back ride this morning. Geez give them one ride on their Birthday and they expect it every year after.   Art
